{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 5,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 279.141,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.997,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then after we had come down",
      "verse": "5:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 2.177,
      "end": 4.313,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "into the wilderness to our father,",
      "verse": "5:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 4.493,
      "end": 6.815,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, he was filled with joy,",
      "verse": "5:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 6.995,
      "end": 8.992,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also my mother, Sariah,",
      "verse": "5:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 9.172,
      "end": 10.658,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "was very glad,",
      "verse": "5:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 10.838,
      "end": 13.253,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for she truly had mourned because of us.",
      "verse": "5:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 13.933,
      "end": 17.462,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For she had supposed that we had perished in the wilderness;",
      "verse": "5:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 17.642,
      "end": 20.428,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and she also had complained against my father,",
      "verse": "5:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 20.608,
      "end": 24.184,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "telling him that he was a visionary man; saying:",
      "verse": "5:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 24.364,
      "end": 27.986,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold you have led us forth from the land of our inheritance,",
      "verse": "5:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 28.166,
      "end": 29.699,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my sons are no more,",
      "verse": "5:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 29.879,
      "end": 32.108,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we perish in the wilderness.",
      "verse": "5:2",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 32.788,
      "end": 35.064,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after this manner of language",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 35.244,
      "end": 37.845,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "had my mother complained against my father.",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 38.525,
      "end": 42.008,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it had come to pass that my father spoke to her, saying:",
      "verse": "5:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 42.188,
      "end": 44.649,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I know that I am a visionary man;",
      "verse": "5:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 44.829,
      "end": 48.033,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for if I had not seen the things of God in a vision",
      "verse": "5:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 48.213,
      "end": 50.86,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I should not have known the goodness of God,",
      "verse": "5:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 51.04,
      "end": 53.083,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but had stayed at Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "5:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 53.263,
      "end": 55.353,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and had perished with my brothers.",
      "verse": "5:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 56.033,
      "end": 58.587,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, I have obtained a land of promise,",
      "verse": "5:5",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 58.767,
      "end": 60.903,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the which things I rejoice;",
      "verse": "5:5",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 61.083,
      "end": 64.148,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, and I know that the Lord will deliver my sons",
      "verse": "5:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 64.328,
      "end": 66.186,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "out of the hands of Laban,",
      "verse": "5:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 66.366,
      "end": 69.895,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and bring them down again to us in the wilderness.",
      "verse": "5:5",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 70.575,
      "end": 72.851,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after this manner of language",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 73.031,
      "end": 77.211,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "did my father, Lehi, comfort my mother, Sariah, concerning us,",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 77.391,
      "end": 81.524,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "while we journeyed in the wilderness up to the land of Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 81.704,
      "end": 83.98,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to obtain the record of the Jews.",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 84.66,
      "end": 88.004,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And when we had returned to the tent of my father,",
      "verse": "5:7",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 88.184,
      "end": 90.227,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold their joy was full,",
      "verse": "5:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 90.407,
      "end": 92.404,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my mother was comforted.",
      "verse": "5:7",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 93.084,
      "end": 94.709,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And she spoke, saying:",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 94.889,
      "end": 96.839,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now I know of a certainty",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 97.019,
      "end": 101.245,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lord has commanded my husband to flee into the wilderness;",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 101.425,
      "end": 104.165,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, and I also know of a certainty",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 104.345,
      "end": 106.574,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lord has protected my sons,",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 106.754,
      "end": 109.633,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and delivered them out of the hands of Laban,",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 109.813,
      "end": 113.25,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and given them power by which they could accomplish the thing",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 113.43,
      "end": 115.38,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which the Lord has commanded them.",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 115.56,
      "end": 118.486,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after this manner of language did she speak.",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 119.166,
      "end": 121.209,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then they did rejoice greatly,",
      "verse": "5:9",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 121.389,
      "end": 124.965,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and offered sacrifice and burnt offerings to the Lord;",
      "verse": "5:9",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 125.145,
      "end": 127.653,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they gave thanks to the God of Israel.",
      "verse": "5:9",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 128.333,
      "end": 131.305,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after they had given thanks to the God of Israel,",
      "verse": "5:10",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 131.485,
      "end": 133.714,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "my father, Lehi, took the records",
      "verse": "5:10",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 133.894,
      "end": 136.913,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were engraved upon the plates of brass,",
      "verse": "5:10",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 137.093,
      "end": 139.647,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he searched them from the beginning.",
      "verse": "5:10",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 140.327,
      "end": 143.81,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he saw that they contained the five books of Moses,",
      "verse": "5:11",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 143.99,
      "end": 147.752,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which gave a record of the creation of the world,",
      "verse": "5:11",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 147.932,
      "end": 149.836,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also of Adam and Eve,",
      "verse": "5:11",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 150.016,
      "end": 152.245,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who were our first parents;",
      "verse": "5:11",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 152.925,
      "end": 156.547,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And also a record of the Jews from the beginning,",
      "verse": "5:12",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 156.727,
      "end": 159.838,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even down to the beginning of the reign of Zedekiah,",
      "verse": "5:12",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 160.018,
      "end": 161.365,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "king of Judah;",
      "verse": "5:12",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 162.045,
      "end": 164.785,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And also the prophecies of the holy prophets,",
      "verse": "5:13",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 164.965,
      "end": 166.312,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the beginning,",
      "verse": "5:13",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 166.492,
      "end": 169.743,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even down to the beginning of the reign of Zedekiah;",
      "verse": "5:13",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 169.923,
      "end": 171.827,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also many prophecies",
      "verse": "5:13",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 172.007,
      "end": 175.211,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which have been spoken by the mouth of Jeremiah.",
      "verse": "5:13",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 175.891,
      "end": 179.606,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then my father, Lehi, also found upon the plates of brass",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 179.786,
      "end": 181.969,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a genealogy of his fathers;",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 182.149,
      "end": 185.214,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so he knew that he was a descendant of Joseph;",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 185.394,
      "end": 188.505,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "indeed, even that Joseph who was the son of Jacob,",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 188.685,
      "end": 190.45,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who was sold into Egypt,",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 190.63,
      "end": 193.324,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and who was preserved by the hand of the Lord,",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 193.504,
      "end": 196.012,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he might preserve his father, Jacob,",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 196.192,
      "end": 197.817,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all his household",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 197.997,
      "end": 199.762,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from perishing with famine.",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 200.442,
      "end": 202.857,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they were also led out of captivity",
      "verse": "5:15",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 203.037,
      "end": 205.08,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and out of the land of Egypt,",
      "verse": "5:15",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 205.26,
      "end": 207.628,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by that same God who had preserved them.",
      "verse": "5:15",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 208.308,
      "end": 210.212,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And thus my father, Lehi,",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 210.392,
      "end": 212.853,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "discovered the genealogy of his fathers.",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 213.033,
      "end": 215.866,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And Laban also was a descendant of Joseph,",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 216.046,
      "end": 218.6,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so he and his fathers had kept the records.",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 219.28,
      "end": 221.509,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now when my father saw all these things,",
      "verse": "5:17",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 221.689,
      "end": 223.732,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he was filled with the Spirit,",
      "verse": "5:17",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 223.912,
      "end": 226.466,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and began to prophesy concerning his seed\u2014",
      "verse": "5:17",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 227.146,
      "end": 229.932,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "That these plates of brass should go forth",
      "verse": "5:18",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 230.112,
      "end": 232.434,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to all nations, kindreds, tongues,",
      "verse": "5:18",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 232.614,
      "end": 235.075,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and people who were of his seed.",
      "verse": "5:18",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 235.755,
      "end": 236.962,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, he said",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 237.142,
      "end": 240.253,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that these plates of brass should never perish;",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 240.433,
      "end": 243.591,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither should they be dimmed any more by time.",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 243.771,
      "end": 246.929,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he prophesied many things concerning his seed.",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 247.609,
      "end": 251.231,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then thus far I and my father had kept the commandments",
      "verse": "5:20",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 251.411,
      "end": 253.501,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with which the Lord had commanded us.",
      "verse": "5:20",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 254.181,
      "end": 256.503,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And we had obtained the records",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 256.683,
      "end": 260.073,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which the Lord had commanded us, and searched them",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 260.253,
      "end": 262.575,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and found that they were desirable;",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 262.755,
      "end": 265.263,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "indeed, even of great worth to us,",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 265.443,
      "end": 270.087,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so much so that we could preserve the commandments of the Lord to our children.",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 270.767,
      "end": 274.807,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, it was wisdom in the Lord that we should carry them with us,",
      "verse": "5:22",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 274.987,
      "end": 278.47,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "as we journeyed in the wilderness towards the land of promise.",
      "verse": "5:22",
      "lineIndex": 98
    }
  ]
}